---
title: Quick Italian Herb, Bacon & Leek Fusilli with Garden Salad & Parmesan Cheese
description: Twirly-wirly pasta mixed in a creamy sauce is too good to be true. There’s plenty of veggies hidden in amongst the fusilli to keep things
fresh and green. For a bit of fun, throw in some diced bacon and leek and you’ve cooked another pasta winning dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-creamy-bacon-garlic-orecchiette-ada84ded.jpg
